The paper deals with monitoring distributed data streams and designing an algorithm to solve the problem while minimizing the amount of messages exchanged between nodes and the coordinator. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AL).
